com.telepathdb.staticparser

Class UnionPuller

  • com.telepathdb.staticparser.UnionPuller

  • public class UnionPuller

    Split a ParseTree on Union into multiple ParseTrees Illustrative example: 'a/(b|c)/d' becomes ['a/b/d', 'a/c/d']

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Static Methods Concrete Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      static java.util.List<com.telepathdb.datamodels.ParseTree> parse()
      Removes the UNION operatorId from a ParseTree. Simply duplicate the tree and on the position of the UNION operatorId, the first tree gets the left-child and the other tree gets the right-child.

    • Method Detail

      • parse

        public static java.util.List<com.telepathdb.datamodels.ParseTree> parse()

        Removes the UNION operatorId from a ParseTree.

        Simply duplicate the tree and on the position of the UNION operatorId, the first tree gets the left-child and the other tree gets the right-child.

        Returns:
        List of ParseTrees each not containing the UNION operatorId.
